	In problems 4#, sketch a graph of the equation in $#R#^3$. Check your answers with <a href="https://www.desmos.com/3d">Desmos 3D</a>.

	#. $$y = x^3$$.

	#. $$z = 2x + 1$$.

	#. $$y^2 + z^2 = 2$$.

	#. $$x^2 + \left( \frac{y}{2} \right)^2 + \left( \frac{z}{3} \right)^2 = 1$$ (hint: think about the graph's intersection with the coordinate planes).	

